data.description: First Right of Refusal! THIS IS IT!! You don't need to look any further. This 4 bedroom 4 bathroom home on 4 acres is remodeled and ready for move in. Large kitchen with Corian countertops, Black Stainless Steel appliances newer cabinets newer flooring. Gas fireplace in the family room with office or playroom attached on lower level. Laundry is on this level with 3/4 bath. Upper level has 3 bedrooms with full bath and primary suite with 3/4 bath en-suite bathroom Main level has another primary suite with walk in closet and 3/4 en-suite bathroom with tiled shower, kitchen, Livingroom and dining room. Basement includes another family room and 2 more rooms for storage or office-playroom or workout rooms. Furnace is new, water heater is one year old. Well tank and pump are new . Outside the home has a covered deck and patio ,yard with sprinkler system Fire pit area, swing set and Trampoline all stay. 2 car attached insulted garage with work area, 4 car detached garage with heat, electric and cement , 8 car outbuilding with electric , cement and pull thru doors. RV hookup. 3 hydrants, some fencing in place. Chicken coop with electric and garden shed. One year old Impact Res Roof and one year old garage door. Come make this your forever home and enjoy the small town life of Strasburg
